.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/121-deep-agent-improvement-benchmark-mode/001-mode-selector-design/decision-record.md:3:description: "Architecture decisions for adding a model/prompt-framework benchmark mode to deep-agent-improvement: mode selector, pluggable seams, reuse map."
