t-improvement-loop has strict single-shot policy with no automated archive (Finding 17)","complete :with-research embeds the full deep-research lock-acquire path (Findings 21-22)","Cross-flow memory-write race exists between deep-review, deep-research, ai-council, and improve (Findings 24-25)"],"ruledOut":["Re-running iter-001 spawn-inventory framing against council/improve assets — near-zero new-info ratio","YAML-runtime timeout_seconds reverse-engineering — out of system-spec-kit scope","permissions-gate.ts as in-scope — iter-002 already established orphaning"],"toolsUsed":["Read","Grep","Glob","Bash"],"sourcesQueried":["commands/deep/assets/deep_start-review-loop_auto.yaml:1-1344","commands/deep/assets/deep_start-research-loop_auto.yaml:105-195","commands/spec_kit/assets/spec_kit_complete_auto.yaml:1-200","commands/deep/assets/deep_start-agent-improvement-loop_auto.yaml:1-216","commands/deep/start-review-loop.md:1-461","agents/ai-council.md:1-779","agents/deep-agent-improvement.md:1-80","skills/sk-ai-council/SKILL.md:1-200","skills/sk-ai-council/scripts/lib/persist-artifacts.js:1-761","skills/sk-ai-council/scripts/lib/audit-trail.js:1-144","skills/deep-review/assets/prompt_pack_iteration.md.tmpl:1"],"executor":{"kind":"cli-claude-code","model":"claude-opus-4-7","reasoningEffort":"high","serviceTier":null},"timestamp":"2026-05-22T06:36:09Z","durationMs":1530000}
