.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/synth-prompt.txt:3:You are consolidating a 20-iteration, 4-model deep-research sweep into one canonical report. The sweep investigated how to design Lane C ("skill-benchmark") for the `deep-improvement` skill (benchmark whether a SKILL is well-structured, well-routed, efficient, and useful in practice — how AIs actually discover/use it — distinct from manual testing playbooks and sk-doc doc-shape validation) PLUS the `deep-agent-improvement` -> `deep-improvement` rename impact map.
