    77	
    78	2. **Tier 2 - Targeted ask** (contract §1): when 1-2 required fields are genuinely ambiguous AND no default exists, emit ONE narrow question per ambiguous field. Command-specific Tier-2-eligible fields (per the Default Resolution Table below): `spec_folder`. **Ordering rule**: none needed. `profile_path` absence is not ambiguity because it has a default, and `executor`/`model` are only required when `grader = llm`.
