    53	## What Was Built
    54	
    55	<!-- Voice guide:
    56	     Open with a hook: what changed and why it matters. One paragraph, impact first.
    57	     Then use ### subsections per feature. Each subsection: what it does + why it exists.
    58	     Write "You can now inspect the trace" not "Trace inspection was implemented."
