     9	
    10	# deep-agent-improvement Scripts: Lane Runtime
    11	
    12	---
    13	
    14	## 1. OVERVIEW
    15	
    16	`scripts/` holds the CLI scripts for the deep-agent-improvement skill. The scripts split into two lanes plus a shared layer. Lane A (`agent-improvement/`) improves an agent file. Lane B (`model-benchmark/`) benchmarks a model or prompt framework. `shared/` serves both lanes, and `lib/` provides CommonJS helpers consumed by the lane scripts.
    17	
    18	Current state:
    19	
    20	- `shared/loop-host.cjs` is the router. It switches between lanes and resolves bare script names to lane directories at spawn time.
    21	- Lane scripts require helpers from `lib/` with relative `../lib/` paths.
    22	- `model-benchmark/run-benchmark.cjs` defaults to `--scorer pattern` and accepts `--scorer 5dim` for the opt-in five-dimension scorer under `model-benchmark/scorer/`.
    23	
    24	---
    25	
    26	## 2. PACKAGE TOPOLOGY
    27	
    28	```text
    29	scripts/
    30	+-- shared/               # Router and cross-lane scripts
    31	|   +-- loop-host.cjs          # Entry point and lane path resolver
    32	|   `-- ...                    # Journal, reducer, fixtures, promotion
    33	+-- agent-improvement/    # Lane A scripts
    34	+-- model-benchmark/      # Lane B scripts
    35	|   `-- scorer/                # Opt-in five-dimension scorer subtree
    36	+-- lib/                  # Shared CommonJS helpers
    37	`-- tests/                # Vitest suites and fixtures
    38	```
    39	
    40	Allowed dependency direction:
    41	
    42	```text
    43	shared/loop-host.cjs → agent-improvement/ | model-benchmark/   (resolved at spawn)
    44	agent-improvement/ → lib/
    45	model-benchmark/ → lib/
    46	shared/ → lib/
    47	```
    48	
    49	---
    50	
    51	## 3. DIRECTORY TREE
    52	
    53	```text
    54	scripts/
    55	+-- shared/
    56	|   +-- loop-host.cjs                      # Mode-switching entry point and lane path resolver
    57	|   +-- improvement-journal.cjs            # Append-only audit journal
    58	|   +-- materialize-benchmark-fixtures.cjs # Fixture materializer
    59	|   +-- mutation-coverage.cjs              # Mutation coverage and dimension trajectories
    60	|   +-- promote-candidate.cjs              # Guarded canonical promotion
    61	|   `-- reduce-state.cjs                    # Dashboard and registry reducer
    62	+-- agent-improvement/
    63	|   +-- score-candidate.cjs                # Dynamic-mode five-dimension candidate scorer
    64	|   +-- benchmark-stability.cjs            # Score variance and weight advisory
    65	|   +-- candidate-lineage.cjs              # Candidate derivation tracking
    66	|   +-- check-mirror-drift.cjs             # Derived-surface drift report
    67	|   +-- generate-profile.cjs               # Dynamic target profile generator
    68	|   +-- rollback-candidate.cjs             # Canonical rollback helper
    69	|   +-- scan-integration.cjs               # Integration surface scanner
    70	|   `-- trade-off-detector.cjs              # Cross-dimension regression detector
    71	+-- model-benchmark/
    72	|   +-- run-benchmark.cjs                  # Fixture and integration scorer
    73	|   +-- dispatch-model.cjs                 # Model-agnostic CLI dispatcher
    74	|   `-- scorer/                             # Opt-in five-dimension scorer subtree
    75	+-- lib/                                   # Shared CommonJS helpers
    76	+-- tests/                                 # Vitest suites and fixtures
    77	`-- vitest.config.mjs                      # Vitest include config
    78	```
    79	
    80	---
    81	
    82	## 4. KEY FILES
    83	
    84	| File | Responsibility |
    85	|---|---|
    86	| `shared/loop-host.cjs` | Mode-switching entry point. `planInvocation` stays byte-identical across lanes and `resolveScriptPath` maps bare names to lane directories at spawn time. |
    87	| `shared/reduce-state.cjs` | Dashboard and experiment registry reducer for both lanes. |
    88	| `shared/promote-candidate.cjs` | Guarded canonical mutation that promotes a winning candidate. |
    89	| `agent-improvement/score-candidate.cjs` | Dynamic-mode five-dimension candidate scorer for Lane A. |
    90	| `agent-improvement/trade-off-detector.cjs` | Cross-dimension regression detection with an insufficient-data guard. |
    91	| `model-benchmark/run-benchmark.cjs` | Fixture and integration scorer. `--scorer pattern` is the default and `--scorer 5dim` selects the `scorer/` subtree. |
    92	| `model-benchmark/dispatch-model.cjs` | Model-agnostic CLI dispatcher for Lane B. |
    93	| `model-benchmark/scorer/` | Five-dimension scorer with `score-model-variant.cjs`, `deterministic/`, `grader/`, and `lib/cache.cjs`. The runtime `cache/` is git-ignored. |
    94	| `lib/` | Shared CommonJS helpers: `typed-errors.cjs`, `promotion-gates.cjs`, `mirror-sync-verify.cjs`. |
    95	
    96	---
    97	
    98	## 5. BOUNDARIES AND FLOW
    99	
   100	| Boundary | Rule |
   101	|---|---|
   102	| Entry | `shared/loop-host.cjs` is the single router. Lanes are not invoked directly by the loop. |
   103	| Imports | Lane and shared scripts import helpers from `lib/` only. `lib/` is not a cross-skill import surface. |
   104	| Lane separation | Lane A scripts stay in `agent-improvement/`, Lane B scripts stay in `model-benchmark/`, and cross-lane scripts stay in `shared/`. |
   105	
   106	Main flow:
   107	
   108	```text
   109	╭──────────────────────────────────────────╮
   110	│ loop dispatch                            │
   111	╰──────────────────────────────────────────╯
   112	                  │
   113	                  ▼
   114	┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐
   115	│ shared/loop-host.cjs (planInvocation)    │
   116	└──────────────────────────────────────────┘
   117	                  │
   118	                  ▼
   119	┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐
   120	│ resolveScriptPath maps bare name to lane │
   121	└──────────────────────────────────────────┘
   122	                  │
   123	        ┌─────────┴─────────┐
   124	        ▼                   ▼
   125	┌───────────────┐   ┌───────────────────┐
   126	│ agent-        │   │ model-benchmark/  │
   127	│ improvement/  │   │ run-benchmark.cjs │
   128	└───────┬───────┘   └─────────┬─────────┘
   129	        │                     │
   130	        └──────────┬──────────┘
   131	                   ▼
   132	        ┌───────────────────┐
   133	        │ lib/ helpers      │
   134	        └───────────────────┘
   135	```
   136	
   137	---
   138	
   139	## 6. VALIDATION
   140	
   141	Run from the `scripts/` directory.
   142	
   143	```bash
   144	npx vitest run
   145	```
   146	
   147	Expected result: every suite under `tests/**/*.vitest.ts` passes.
   148	
   149	List the source files from the repository root.
   150	
   151	```bash
   152	rg --files .opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts -g '!node_modules'
   153	```
   154	
