.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:766:The feature catalog root is `.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/feature_catalog/feature_catalog.md`. Use it as the current-state capability index when a scenario needs source-of-truth feature context beyond the command transcript.
