+
+# Actions Taken
+
+- Read the active `deep-agent-improvement` skill contract, especially lane routing, resource maps, runtime assets, and the shared candidate/dispatcher/scorer seams.
+- Scanned exact-string references for `deep-agent-improvement`, `deep-improvement`, related command names, and runtime mirror paths across `.opencode`, `.claude`, `.codex`, `.gemini`, root docs, install guides, and spec metadata.
+- Read the Phase 122 parent and Phase 002 rename scaffold to align this impact map with the planned phase order and success criteria.
